<h1>What</h1>
<p>BitcoinExchange is a marketplace to exhange US dollars for bitcoins.</p>
<h1>Why</h1>
<p>BitcoinExhange aims to be the easiest solution for aquiring bitcoins. It is meant to lower the barrier to entry into the bitcoin currency. Transactions must be $20 USD or less. For larger transactions and more features <%= link_to 'Coinbase.com', 'https://coinbase.com/' %> is recommened.</p>

<h1>How do I know this isn't a scam?</h1>
<p>The short answer is you don't. A list of <%= link_to 'all the transactions', transactions_path %> carried out on BitcoinExchange is publicly available. The source code to the site is also publicly available. Check external sources to verify that this is a legitmate exchange.</p>
<h1>Open Source</h1>
<p>Bitcoin exchange is open source. The source code is available <%= link_to 'on github', 'https://www.github.com/masonforest/bitcoin-exchange' %>. Please contribute back! You can also run your own bitcoin exchange for profit!</p>
